# Task 5 - Advanced Features

## Overview

This project was developed as part of the ApexPlanet Web Development Internship. The objective of this task was to enhance the User Management System by adding advanced functionality such as user roles, profile management, and additional dashboard features.

## Features Implemented

### User Roles

* Added role column in database
* Default role assigned as User during registration
* Role information displayed in profile page

### Profile Management

* View personal information
* Display Name
* Display Email
* Display Phone Number
* Display Address
* Display User Role

### Weather Information Module

* Dedicated weather information page
* Dashboard navigation support
* Additional feature integration

### Dashboard Enhancements

* Profile Button
* Weather Button
* Improved Navigation
* Bootstrap Icons

## Technologies Used

* PHP
* MySQL
* HTML5
* CSS3
* Bootstrap 5
* Bootstrap Icons

## Files Created

* profile.php
* weather.php

## Files Modified

* register.php
* dashboard.php

